  "id": "RAW_0c1a1a0a",
  "title": "AI 又要颠覆数学？陶哲轩紧急发声：停止造神！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkyNjU2ODM2NQ==&mid=2247623773&idx=3&sn=715c35dd78a8c63a65fe7230b375b072",
  "date": "2026-01-12 01:56:00",
  "author": "硅星人Pro",
  "siteName": "硅星人Pro",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"100140088\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e815cb98&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FjopKOlhibRBI9eShzXLIf8dzuPu6NXfx1G1gsIwgBGQ1pic6X1Vx7nPvUic19DvG48xxlM00ic3baTogpkFkPWF9YA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"visibility:visible;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21frh\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mkaho4tfqam\" style=\"font-size: 13px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkaho4tj1n4c\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">文章转载于新智元</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"visibility:visible;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21frh\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">你可能刷到过这种极具煽动性的新闻标题：「AI完全自主解决了人类五十年未解的数学难题！数学家要失业了！」</span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility:visible;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2lfb\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">对于渴望见证AGI诞生的人来说，这无疑又是一剂强心针。而对于坚守人类智力尊严的数学家而言，这仿佛是最后堡垒陷落的警报。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"visibility:visible;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2nxz\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">随着这些文章的影响力越来越大，终于有人坐不住了，出手降温。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee217d4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">有趣的是，这个人正是AI数学研究最积极的推动者之一——陶哲轩。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2daz\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">陶哲轩并没有否定AI的数学研究能力，他只是想把水温调回现实。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21q2e\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">就在今天凌晨，陶哲轩发帖称，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;\">AI解决数学问题的能力被断章取义地夸大了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"292\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"608\" data-imgfileid=\"505180124\" data-ratio=\"0.5194444444444445\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1170\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=076ed586&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3nP55dAIkHxN3qm2mibCptEwC27Vw8LOQuxyysKWdSN5GXmc3noDAPkJWy2FhdLGUTYMERXgdmqsQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D1\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21hx2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">他在Erdős Problems项目相关的GitHub页面补充了更系统的说明与警示。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee215j4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">他强调外界对AI解决Erdős问题的解读很容易过度，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;\">尤其是把某个孤立战果当成「AI已具备高级数学能力」的证据。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21j53\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">陶哲轩到底在澄清什么？AI在Erdős问题上究竟做到了什么程度？</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">陶哲轩的深夜辟谣</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2w8k\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">首先要说的是，陶哲轩并不是否认AI在数学上的进步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee29k9\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">他否认的主要是一种偷懒叙事：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;\">把「AI在某些问题上能产出可验证结果」，偷换成「AI已经会做数学、能独立创新、能替代人类」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee215sh\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">在他更新的「AI contributions to Erdős problems」页面里表示，看AI在Erdős问题上的成绩单时，千万别只盯着「解了多少题」，还特别注意下面几点：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2kch\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">题目难度差得离谱，「解题数」不能直接比：</span><span textstyle=\"\">Erdős问题的难度跨度非常夸张，一端是公认超级硬核的核心难题，另一端是大量长期没人细查、研究很少的「长尾题」。后者里有不少其实属于「低垂果实」，更适合当前AI工具发挥。问题是：你很难在不做专家级文献梳理的前提下，提前判断一题属于哪一类。所以，拿「谁解得多」来PK，很可能不是同一难度段的对比。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2x2p\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">很多题目「是否未解」本身就不确定：</span><span textstyle=\"\">网站上不少问题缺少系统文献回顾，因此「Open」（未解）这个标签往往只是暂定。AI解出一题后，大家往往很快发现——</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\">原来文献里早有人解过</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\">（可能方法略不同）。这会让「AI首解」的叙事非常容易翻车。</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2cvt\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">我们看到的多是成功案例，失败被隐藏了：</span><span textstyle=\"\">网站对AI工具的记录并不完整，尤其对没进展、失败尝试的记录更少。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21e84\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">有些题目原始表述有误，可能被「钻字面漏洞」解掉：</span><span textstyle=\"\">极少数情况下，Erdős的题目表述可能不严谨甚至有误，要还原本意，往往需要结合上下文、靠领域经验做判断——这一步带有一定主观性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2zpd\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">数学价值不只在答案，更在「连接知识网络」：</span><span textstyle=\"\">数学的意义不只是证明成立，还在于这件事对相关领域有什么启发？和已有理论怎么挂钩？有哪些可迁移的方法？人类写证明时，往往会自然补上这些旁白：背景、动机、文献对比、方法边界。但</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\">AI</span></span></strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\">主导的证明</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\">常常缺少这层知识的光晕，结果可能技术上对，但对数学共同体的可用价值更低。</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2euf\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">解出冷门长尾题，不等于够格投顶级期刊：</span><span textstyle=\"\">不是每解一个未解题都等价于可发表论文。尤其当题目本身很冷门、方法只是对已有套路的小改动时，更未必能进好期刊。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"font-size:15px;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21b58\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">把AI生成的证明形式化到Lean这类证明助手里，是提高可信度的好办法，但仍可能被钻空子。</span><span textstyle=\"\">比如形式化时偷偷引入额外公理、问题陈述被误形式化、或者利用数学库/语法的某些「边角行为」。特别是当形式化证明</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\">短得离谱</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\">或</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\">啰嗦得异常</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\">时，更要警惕。</span></span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee216o5\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">简单来说，陶哲轩认为AI在Erdős问题上的进展值得关注，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;\">但真正要看的是题目的难度层级、文献核查、题意还原、知识融入，以及验证链条是否扎实等更多维度的指标。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2yza\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">AI能做出成果不等于AI已具备完整数学能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;text-align:center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"654\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1722\" data-imgfileid=\"505180126\" data-ratio=\"1.163888888888889\" style=\"width: 335px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1480\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8f52f2cb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3nP55dAIkHxN3qm2mibCptEibaJT1B3A3ibBxbLx12iagoZAjZooGwCDjUSwxTMyqgcCRG9Ce9IRibCIw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D3\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI不是数学家 &nbsp;而是工具链的一环</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2b0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">那现实里，AI到底做了什么？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee215p0\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">陶哲轩的这份GitHub页面把AI贡献分成了多个类别。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee215p4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">有AI生成了完整（或部分）解答，有AI以为题目未解、结果发现文献早就解过的案例，有AI参与文献检索，有AI把证明形式化到 Lean，有AI帮人类重写既有论证，等等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2sy4\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">例如，页面列出&nbsp;</span><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mk9b64qz-kpw94q\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">#728问题</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">&nbsp;在2026年1月6日由Aristotle与ChatGPT 5.2 Pro 给出完整解答（Lean验证），</span></span><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mk9b64qz-56mpax\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">#729问题</span></a></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">在1月8-10日也获得完整解答（Lean验证）。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21ash\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">这意味着在某些题型、某些难度区间，AI确实能做出「可运行的证明结构」，甚至进入形式化验证流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"148\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"468\" data-imgfileid=\"505180123\" data-ratio=\"0.2638888888888889\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1774\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7129adbc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3nP55dAIkHxN3qm2mibCptEUYHstOyAa3EV8ficWlDup9JzyULCicqotlsbcGQbp5XJClbSbcCX9uHg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D5\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2tq2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">有些问题完全由AI解决，但后来才发现，有人早就解决了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"549\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1470\" data-imgfileid=\"505180125\" data-ratio=\"0.9777777777777777\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1504\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c21b452c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3nP55dAIkHxN3qm2mibCptEU7l3o9922ckPicINic9ImckOZNkF3flZiaGZQmOdjLK21O1iaCprE56v9A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D6\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21b8t\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">陶哲轩还专门列了「AI-powered literature review（AI驱动的文献回顾）」一类：AI被用来搜索是否已有结果、是否存在误判Open的情况。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:24px;margin-right:8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-backh=\"422\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1404\" data-imgfileid=\"505180127\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" style=\"width: 661px !important;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1872\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=645e0a26&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUicQ7HgWiaUb3nP55dAIkHxN3qm2mibCptEgQJNXK0qCUYncha2KVVWXSwGkyeGPciaLOWFRtu1zdafF9hdAoJseVg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%26watermark%3D1%26tp%3Dwxpic%26wxfrom%3D5%26wx_lazy%3D1%23imgIndex%3D7\"></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;letter-spacing: inherit;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px -30px;padding: 0px;hyphens: auto;letter-spacing: inherit;font-size: 16px;color: transparent;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: justify;width: 30px;height: 30px;border-radius: 50%;background: rgba(1, 169, 216, 0.3);overflow: hidden;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"padding:0px 0px 24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 15px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:inherit;font-size:20px;line-height:1.75em;hyphens:auto;text-align:justify;\">人类仍然是主角</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21q3a\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">如果仅凭几个孤例就认为「AI数学无敌」，显然有些片面。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee224n6\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">但反过来，觉得AI做数学啥也不行，同样会错过它真正有价值的部分。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2dvh\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">更准确的说法可能是：AI正在学会做数学的体力活和工程活：跑套路、补漏洞、做形式化、写稿改稿、查文献。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee2no5\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:1px;\">而数学真正的「灵魂」——提出深刻问题、创造新概念、把一个结果嵌进整个学科的知识网络——仍然高度依赖人类。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee290x\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">所以，陶哲轩这次深夜发帖想要说的，正在于此。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21rro\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">未来的数学家，或许不再是孤独的思考者，而是统领着硅基智能大军的指挥官：在那片广袤的数学原野上，人类指引方向，AI开路架桥。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:16px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21xy4\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing:1px;\">别断章取义地神话AI，但也绝不要低估这股正在重塑真理探索方式的力量。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:8px;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, -apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:8px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahlee21l8c\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mkahpnuwd5r\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahpnusxtw\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">参考资料：</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:14px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mkahpnus16w\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://mathstodon.xyz/@tao/115871649394962391\" target=\"_blank\">https://mathstodon.xyz/@tao/115871649394962391</a></span></span></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "陶哲轩辟谣 AI 在数学研究中被“造神”的现象，强调 AI 是强大的工具而非独立的数学家，呼吁客观看待其真实能力与局限性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "陶哲轩辟谣 AI 在数学研究中被“造神”的现象，强调 AI 是强大的工具而非独立的数学家，呼吁客观看待其真实能力与局限性。",
  "summary": "本文围绕数学家陶哲轩对 AI 在数学研究中被过度“造神”的现象进行辟谣。文章指出，尽管 AI 在解决 Erdős 问题上取得了一些进展，但其能力被夸大了。陶哲轩强调，AI 目前更多是作为工具，能解决一些难度较低或“长尾”问题，辅助文献检索和形式化证明，而非具备独立的数学创新能力。他澄清了外界对 AI 解决数学难题的误解，例如：题目难度差异大、旧有难题被误认为 AI 首解、成功案例被放大而失败被隐藏等。文章总结认为，AI 是数学研究工具链的重要组成部分，能够承担“体力活”和“工程活”，但提出深层次问题、创造新概念等“灵魂”工作仍高度依赖人类，呼吁客观看待 AI 在数学领域的作用。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 在数学领域的进展被过度夸大和“造神”，尤其在未经专家级验证的情境下。",
      "explanation": "陶哲轩通过分析 Erdős 问题为例，指出外界常忽略问题难度差异、旧有解决方案、以及 AI 失败案例，导致对 AI 能力产生不切实际的期望。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 在数学研究中扮演的是强大的“工具”角色，而非独立创新的“数学家”。",
      "explanation": "AI 擅长执行重复性、工程性的任务，如生成可验证的证明结构、辅助文献检索和形式化证明，但其提出的问题深度和知识网络连接能力仍有欠缺。"
    },
    {
      "point": "数学的真正价值在于概念创新与知识网络构建，这仍高度依赖人类数学家。",
      "explanation": "文章强调，数学不仅是找到答案，更在于其对相关领域的启发和知识的融会贯通，AI 目前在此方面尚不能取代人类的独特作用。"
    },
    {
      "point": "应以客观、平衡的态度看待 AI，既不盲目崇拜，也不低估其潜力。",
      "explanation": "文章主张，AI 是正在重塑真理探索方式的力量，应充分利用其优势，让其作为人类指挥下的强大助手，共同探索数学前沿。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "他否认的主要是一种偷懒叙事：把「AI 在某些问题上能产出可验证结果」，偷换成「AI 已经会做数学、能独立创新、能替代人类」。",
    "数学价值不只在答案，更在「连接知识网络」：数学的意义不只是证明成立，还在于这件事对相关领域有什么启发？",
    "AI 能做出成果不等于 AI 已具备完整数学能力。",
    "更准确的说法可能是：AI 正在学会做数学的体力活和工程活：跑套路、补漏洞、做形式化、写稿改稿、查文献。",
    "但反过来，觉得 AI 做数学啥也不行，同样会错过它真正有价值的部分。"
  ],
